ient Portal (+ Website)\",\"point10\":\"Patient Mobile App (Android \u0026 iOS)\",\"point11\":\"Provider Mobile App (Android \u0026 iOS)\",\"point12\":\"Patient Health Blog\"},\"price_1\":{\"title\":\"Monthly\",\"billed\":\"Billed monthly\"},\"price_12\":{\"title\":\"Annual\",\"billed\":\"Billed annually\"},\"inclusive_1\":\"Includes\",\"inclusive_2\":\"Team Users\"},\"Pro\":{\"title\":\"Pro\",\"subtitle\":\"Advanced Patient Engagement\",\"credits\":25,\"feature_heading\":\"Features\",\"features\":{\"point1\":\"Everything in Standard +\",\"point2\":\"Remote Patient Monitoring\",\"point3\":\"Health Device Integrations\",\"point4\":\"Asynchronous Text Consults\",\"point5\":\"Custom AI Note Templates\",\"point6\":\"Health Journal\",\"point7\":\"Instant Video Calls\",\"point8\":\"Payment Credits\",\"point9\":\"Patient Feedback \u0026 Testimonials\"},\"price_1\":{\"title\":\"Monthly\",\"billed\":\"Billed monthly\"},\"price_12\":{\"title\":\"Annual\",\"billed\":\"Billed annually\"},\"inclusive_1\":\"Includes\",\"inclusive_2\":\"Team Users\",\"additional_1\":\"Additional\",\"additional_2\":\"Team Users\"},\"Premium\":{\"title\":\"Premium\",\"subtitle\":\"For Clinics Needing Great Configurability\",\"credits\":50,\"feature_heading\":\"Features\",\"features\":{\"point1\":\"Everything in Pro +\",\"point2\":\"Custom Email Domain\",\"point3\":\"Custom Notifications (SMS/Email/WhatsApp)\",\"point4\":\"Upto 10 Practice Locations\",\"point5\":\"Assisted Video Consultations\",\"point6\":\"Discount Coupons\",\"point7\":\"Advanced Patient Registration Settings\",\"point8\":\"Multiple Currencies \u0026 Payment Gateways\",\"point9\":\"Patient Support Chat\",\"point10\":\"Community AI Templates - coming soon\"},\"price_1\":{\"title\":\"Monthly\",\"billed\":\"Billed monthly\"},\"price_12\":{\"title\":\"Annual\",\"billed\":\"Billed annually\"},\"inclusive_1\":\"Includes\",\"inclusive_2\":\"Team Users\",\"additional_1\":\"Additional\",\"additional_2\":\"Team Users\"},\"enterprise_basic\":{\"title\":\"Enterprise Basic\",\"for\":\"Essentials for Healthcare Startups\",\"feature_heading\":\"The features available in Enterprise Basic\",\"points\":{\"point1\":\"White-labelled Patient Web-interface\",\"point2\":\"Telemedicine, Video, Text, RPA\",\"point3\":\"Appointments, Payments \u0026 Clinical Notes\",\"point4\":\"Multi-language support\"}},\"enterprise_standard\":{\"title\":\"Enterprise Standard\",\"for\":\"Professional Plans for Startups \u0026 Healthcare Services\",\"recommend\":\"RECOMMENDED\",\"feature_heading\":\"The features available in Enterprise Standard\",\"points\":{\"point1\":\"All the features available in Enterprise Basic, Plus\",\"point2\":\"White-labelled Provider Web Interface\",\"point3\":\"Provider Self-Signup\",\"point4\":\"Payment Credit Management\"}},\"enterprise_hosted\":{\"title\":\"Enterprise Premium\",\"for\":\"Premium Plans for Startups \u0026 Healthcare Services\",\"feature_heading\":\"The features available in Enterprise Premium\",\"contact_btn\":\"Contact Us\",\"points\":{\"point1\":\"All the features available in Enterprise Standard, Plus\",\"point2\":\"Independent Hosting in AWS\",\"point3\":\"Fully Managed Service\",\"point4\":\"Dedicated Data Storage\"}},\"testimonials\":{\"testimonials1\":\"I’ve been using the Virtual Practice app since 2020, and I was impressed with the interface from the very beginning. Over the years, the platform’s stability and absence of downtimes have truly set it apart. Their support team is exceptional and always responsive, making it a reliable partner for my practice.\",\"name1\":\"Dr. Joseph Crooks\",\"position1\":\"General Practitioner, Trinidad \u0026 Tobago\",\"testimonials3\":\"The system is user-friendly, reliable, and perfectly suited to the needs of a modern medical practice.\",\"name3\":\"Internal Medicine Specialist\",\"position3\":\"Private Practice, Caribbean\",\"testimonials5\":\"Allowing doctors to offer telemedicine, remote monitoring health plans, collect payments and the health blog are some of the best features of the Virtual Practice®.\",\"name5\":\"Dr. Gerard Saltibus MD\",\"position5\":\"General Practitioner, St. Lucia\"},\"faq\":{\"title\":\"Frequently Asked Questions\",\"T_1\":\"Trial\",\"Q_1\":\"How do I sign up?\",\"A_1\":\"To sign up for a Virtual Practice account,\",\"A_1_1\":\" click here\",\"A_1_2\":\" or find the 'Start Free Trial' button on our homepage. You'll have a 14-day trial to explore the platform's features before choosing a subscription plan. To continue using the service without interruption, we recommend upgrading your account before the trial expires.\",\"Q_2\":\"What happens after the trial ends?\",\"A_2\":\"After the 14-day trial, your account will be temporarily deactivated for 30 days. During this period,your data remains secure, and you can still log in to subscribe and reactivate services instantly. After 30 days, if no subscription is chosen, your account and data will be permanently deleted. We'll send reminders to help you stay informed as the trial period ends.\",\"Q_3\":\"Is the application white-labelled during the trial?\",\"A_3\":\"White-labelling is offered exclusively with our Enterprise plans, as it involves a custom setup process that can only be initiated once you subscribe. While the trial does not include white-labelling, you will still have full access to all other features. For a detailed overview of white-label customization,please contact our support team.\",\"T_2\":\"Subscription\",\"Q_4\":\"How can I pay for my Virtual Practice?\",\"A_4\":\"You can choose a billing option (eg., annual, semi-annual billing) and pay for a subscription plan of your choice by credit or debit card. To pay for a subscription plan, access Settings \u003e Virtual Practice Subscription \u003e Virtual Practice Plans on your Virtual Practice Manager. Subscription payments can be done before or after the expiry of your free trial.\",\"Q_5\":\"Can I upgrade or downgrade my subscription?\",\"A_5\":\"Yes, you can upgrade or downgrade your subscription anytime. If you downgrade, any remaining credits from your current billing cycle will be applied to your new plan, but please note that there are no refunds for downgrades. If you upgrade, you will be immediately billed for the price difference between your current and new plans until the next billing cycle.\",\"Q_6\":\"Who are Team users? Do I pay for each Team user? \",\"A_6\":\"Team users are the healthcare providers, nurses, administrators, or other team members within your organization who each have their own login to the Virtual Practice Manager. Each subscription plan includes a set number of team users. Patient users, however, are unlimited and free on all plans.\",\"Q_7\":\"When we need to add additional Team users, how is that billed?\",\"A_7\":\"Additional team users can be added at any time. You will be billed for each new user as soon as they are added to your Virtual Practice.\",\"Q_8\":\"What payment methods are accepted?\",\"A_8\":\"We accept credit and debit cards for subscription payments.\",\"T_3\":\"Mobile Apps\",\"Q_9\":\"I would like to have a custom-branded patient mobile app. How do I proceed?\",\"A_9\":\"If your plan includes this option, you can add a custom-branded patient mobile app as an add-on. The add-on is priced at $1188 per year for both Android and iOS, with an annual payment. If you need an Android-only version, it is available for $1008 per year.\",\"A_9_1\":\"Contact us\",\"A_9_2\":\" for more information.\",\"Q_10\":\"Are the patient and provider mobile apps available in all plans?\",\"A_10\":\"Yes, the generic mobile applications (ContinuousCare Patient mobile application and the Virtual Practice Provider mobile application) are available in all plans. The white-labelled versions of these mobile apps are available as add-ons in certain plans.\",\"T_4\":\"Video \u0026 SMS Pricing\",\"Q_11\":\"Is there an additional cost for Video Consultation streaming?\",\"A_11\":\"Video streaming charges are applicable. The cost is USD0.005225 per streamed subscribed minute. Streamed subscribed minutes applies to the duration of time during which both participants are subscribing to each other's video stream. These costs only apply for actual sessions, with both participants involved. It will not apply if one participant starts streaming video but the other participant has not joined the call. So, for a video session of 15 minutes duration, the total streamed subscribed minutes = 2 x 15. The total cost of a 15 minute video session is thus: USD 0.005225/min x 2 x 15 = USD 0.15675. Overall usage costs will be invoiced at the end of every month, if applicable.\",\"Q_12\":\"What are the additional costs for SMS Usage?\",\"A_12_3\":\"SMS charges apply for all messages sent from your Virtual Practice, including automated alerts and custom messages. The cost of each SMS depends on the recipient's location, and note that 1 SMS equals 160 characters. For instance, a 300-character message will be billed as two SMS messages.\",\"A_12_4\":\"If you use the platform's default SMS gateway, applicable SMS charges will be invoiced monthly. You also have the option to connect your own SMS account and handle billing directly with your SMS provider. Certain notifications can be turned off as needed. Contact us for more information.\",\"A_12_5\":\"Additionally, you can opt to turn off certain notifications in your Virtual Practice.\",\"A_12_1\":\"Contact us\",\"A_12_2\":\" should you have any questions.\",\"T_5\":\"Website Integrations\",\"Q_13\":\"I want to use my own domain instead of the ContinuousCare subdomain. Is that possible?\",\"A_13\":\"Yes, we do support mapping of a custom domain to the patient portal website which allows you to use your own domain e.g. www.yourcompanyname.com instead of yourcompanyname.continuouscare.io. Once you have taken up a paid subscription, contact our support team and we will guide you through the process. For more information on mapping your own domain to your patient portal,\",\"A_13_1\":\" click here.\",\"Q_14\":\"Can the platform be integrated with my existing website ?\",\"A_14\":\"Yes, the subdomain or domain of your website can be mapped to your Virtual Practice.\",\"A_14_1\":\" Learn more\",\"A_14_2\":\" about mapping your website to your Virtual Practice.\",\"T_6\":\"White-labelling\",\"Q_15\":\"What does white-labelling the Virtual Practice mean?\",\"A_15\":\"White-labelling the Virtual Practice would mean integrating your brand into the telemedicine platform under your chosen domain, with the removal of any 'ContinuousCare' references. To learn more about white-labelling your Virtual Practice,\",\"A_15_1\":\" click here.\",\"Q_16\":\"Can I get the Virtual Practice white-labelled in my Business name?\",\"A_16\":\"Yes, we offer white-labelling of the Virtual Practice in our Enterprise plans.\",\"T_7\":\"Languages\",\"Q_17\":\"What languages are currently supported in the platform?\",\"A_17\":\"We currently support English and Spanish in the patient interfaces (Web Patient Portal and custom-branded patient mobile app) of the Virtual Practice. Supported languages other than English, are enabled based on request. Please note that translations are currently sourced from customers for optimal suitability to context. Customers can review the translations and provide feedback regarding the translation accuracy in the interfaces. There is no additional charge for availing of supported languages.\",\"A_17_1\":\" Contact us\",\"A_17_2\":\" to discuss your requirements.\",\"T_8\":\"More questions?\",\"A_18\":\"Visit our\",\"A_18_1\":\" help center\",\"A_18_2\":\" for more information. You can also reach out to\",\"A_18_3\":\" our support team\",\"A_18_4\":\". We're here to help.\",\"T_10\":\"Credits\",\"Q_10_1\":\"What is a credit?\",\"A_10_1\":\"A credit is a digital token that allows you to use specific usage-based features within the Virtual Practice, such as AI-powered tools, with each credit representing a unit of feature usage that gets deducted from your account when the feature is used.\",\"Q_10_2\":\"Do I get free credits?\",\"A_10_2\":\"Yes you do get a certain amount of credits allocated to your account every month when your Virtual Practice is on an active subscription. These monthly credits expire at the end of each monthly subscription cycle.\",\"A_10_2_1\":\"New customers also get some free credits to use during their trial of the Virtual Practice.\",\"Q_10_3\":\"How do I purchase additional credits?\",\"A_10_3\":\"Credits can be purchased using your credit cards through our secure payment processor. All payment information is encrypted and never stored on our platform. Access the Manage Credits view in your Virtual Practice to manage and pay for additional credits. An active Virtual Practice subscription to purchase and use credits.\",\"Q_10_4\":\"What happens if I run out of credits?\",\"A_10_4\":\"AI-powered features like AI Scribe and AI Transcribe will become unavailable until you purchase more credits or your monthly credits refresh. You should monitor your credits usage in the Manage Credits dashboard in your Virtual Practice.\",\"Q_10_5\":\"Do purchased credits expire?\",\"A_10_5\":\"No, purchased credits never expire. Only monthly credits included in your subscription expire at the end of each billing cycle.\",\"Q_10_6\":\"How are credits deducted?\",\"A_10_6\":\"Credits are deducted each time you use an AI feature. Monthly credits are used first, followed by purchased credits. The exact amount depends on the specific feature and usage.\",\"Q_10_7\":\"Can I get a refund for unused credits?\",\"A_10_7\":\"Purchased credits are non-refundable. However, please contact our support team for billing issues if any. All credits purchase and usage are defined in our Subscription \u0026 Credits Payment Terms.\",\"Q_10_8\":\"How do I track which features use the most credits?\",\"A_10_8\":\"The Credit Usage Chart in your dashboard shows a breakdown of credit consumption by feature, helping you understand your usage patterns.\"},\"Basic.title\":\"Basic.title\",\"Basic.subtitle\":\"Basic.subtitle\",\"ai_scribe_intro\":\"Introducing AI Scribe\",\"billing\":{\"monthly\":\"Monthly\",\"annually\":\"Annually\",\"quarterly\":\"Quarterly\",\"semi_annual\":\"Semi-Annual\",\"annual\":\"Annual\",\"biennial\":\"Biennial\",\"triennial\":\"Triennial\",\"save\":\"Save\"},\"additional_info\":{\"need_credits\":\"Need more Credits?\",\"purchase_credits\":\"Purchase additional credits anytime\",\"to_power\":\"to power your AI Scribe features.\",\"feature_comparison\":\"See the feature comparison\"},\"testimonials_section\":{\"title\":\"See what our customers have to say!\"},\"cta_section\":{\"title\":\"Sign up for Free Trial\",\"subtitle\":\"Transform your healthcare business today in a few easy steps\",\"button\":\"Try it FREE for 14 days\"}}}}]\n"])</script></body></html>